data.description: Welcome to the Southland! This highly sought after, swim, tennis, golf and lake community is second to none. This charming 4 sided brick home features 4 bedrooms, a bonus room, a grand foyer leading to a spacious quest bedroom on the main, and gourmet kitchen, with white cabinets, a cooktop stove, and a breakfast area with plenty of natural light. The vaulted family room has skylights, and a brick fireplace with back stairs leading to the upper level. There is a partially finished basement with endless design opportunities. This home exudes sophistication and luxury. It boast elegant chandeliers in just about every room and is waiting for you to make it your home!
